The paper discusses the use of IoT in the automotive industry, specifically in the context of VANETs. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also focuses on security protocols, which suggests that it could belong to cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) or cs.SY (Systems and Control). Additionally, the paper mentions simulation analysis, which could place it in cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) or cs.IT (Information Theory).
